{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"d7b211527b","title":"对空军再次击落敌U-2飞机的报告的批语","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"87c3f332e0","index":0,"year":1964,"month":7,"day":21,"articleId":"d7b211527b"}],"tags":[{"id":"9bc2c334c7","name":"批示","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji46","name":"毛泽东全集第46卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/46-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji46":{"comments":[{"id":"ab6ed0f2c3","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d7b211527b","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这个批语写在中国人民解放军空军司令员刘亚楼1964年7月18日关于请公安部副部长、中共中央办公厅警卫局局长江东兴将空军再次击落敌U-2飞机的报告转送毛泽东的信上"},{"id":"c89fe382ae","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d7b211527b","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"指中国人民解放军空军司令员刘亚楼、政治委员徐深吉、副司令员王辉球1964年7月17日关于再次击落敌U-2飞机给中国人民解放军总参课长罗瑞卿并报中央军委副主席林彪和中央军委的报告。报告在详细介绍空军七月七日在漳州击落故U-2飞机的情况后，总结了这次战斗的一些新特点、新经验以及在党政军民密切合作下，从军事、政治、技术三方面采取的一系列有力措施等。"}],"contents":[{"id":"9f3f040957","type":"title","text":"对空军再次击落敌U-2飞机的报告的批语”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d7b211527b"},{"id":"ab6ed0f2c3","type":"paragraph","text":"刘亚楼同志：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d7b211527b"},{"id":"c89fe382ae","type":"paragraph","text":"此件看过，很好，向同志们致以祝贺","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d7b211527b"},{"id":"46aacec75c","type":"paragraph","text":"毛泽东","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d7b211527b"},{"id":"1e0231533f","type":"paragraph","text":"七月廿一日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d7b211527b"}],"page":{"id":"8e95887864","publicationId":"maoquanji46","articleId":"d7b211527b","start":513,"end":513}}}},"__N_SSG":true}